title: ubuntu xenial [Running] - Oracle VM VirtualBox_166.png
description:
One of the nice bits of budgie but you may not be aware of is that you can pin applications to the panel - just launch your app and then right-click the panel icon and choose the pin option.

To help making this capability discoverable I've pushed a change that will be coming done the wires so that for new users - Files, Firefox, Libreoffice-Writer, Gnome-Software are pinned automatically.
